track.name: Fish & Bird
comments: the ocean is filled with tears...
One of my absolute favorite songs ever. Stunning.
I did a little illustration based on this song at http://www.stickygum.com/pictures/illustrations/fish-and-bird but the song is just so achingly beautiful it's hard to do justice to.
I love this song so much, it's actually kind of ridiculous.
This and Flowers Grave almost have me in tears. So beautiful.
This song is about Lewis Carrol's love for Alice. slightly paedophilic undertones to the song imo. Or it could just be about impossible/forbidden love, very sad song either way
But the ocean is filled with tears.
This song is beyond beautiful... it always makes me so sad.
